Package: MatrixEffects
Title: L2 Norm Tests for Matrix Effects in Non-Linear Calibration Curves
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mathias", "Brevik", email = "mathias.brevik@uib.no", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Statistical tests for detecting matrix effects in quadratic and four-parameter 
    logistic calibration curves using L2 norm distances. Implements the methodology from 
    Brevik et al. (2026) for robust matrix effect assessment in analytical chemistry.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: 
    sandwich,
    minpack.lm
Suggests: 
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
URL: https://github.com/BrevikM/MatrixEffects
